<a href="/questions/1339881-how-is-this-book-for-young-readers">how is this book for young readers?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1339881'><a id="like_count_community_question_1339881" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1339881?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">4 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F35995489-the-extraordinary-life-of-sam-hell">like</a></span>

