        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2417964473" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17308961070791358318">Sam Hill was born with red eyes. His mother, a woman of deep faith, deemed him extraordinary and believed he would lead an extraordinary life. Sam, however, felt anything but. He struggled to find meaning among the mishaps and tragedies throughout his life.<br/><br/>I was immediately drawn into this story and some of the amazing characters. Sam&apos;s mom was my favorite. There were some really funny and also heartbreaking moments as well. This is definitely one of the best novels that I&apos;ve read so far this ye</span>
  <span id="freeText17308961070791358318" style="display:none">Sam Hill was born with red eyes. His mother, a woman of deep faith, deemed him extraordinary and believed he would lead an extraordinary life. Sam, however, felt anything but. He struggled to find meaning among the mishaps and tragedies throughout his life.<br /><br />I was immediately drawn into this story and some of the amazing characters. Sam's mom was my favorite. There were some really funny and also heartbreaking moments as well. This is definitely one of the best novels that I've read so far this year! </span>
